latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Happieesttt birthday my lovee🎂🥳🎉❤️❤️❤️. You’re irritating me since 2002 😂😂 but you also got my back ❤️. You’re my partner in everything ❤️❤️. You may look small but you’ve got the biggest heart and this is probably your biggest flaw as well❤️❤️. You are so special in my life, not only for being my lovely sister, but also for being one of my best friends. Without you I would have not made this far🥺❤️.I love you sooo much bacchiiiii😘😘❤️❤️❤️I’m so glad to have a great sister like you, though I’m not counting but you keep getting better always.💕❤️. We shared so many laughs and thoughts and also boosted each other up when we were down.🔥🔥❤️ Just be yourself always, don’t think about others and what you should always know is I am there for you.💋🥰💞❤️❤️ May you achieve whatever you truly desire ❤️. I love you sooo sooo much baby ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️ Stay blessed my loveee💋💋💞💞❤️❤️
Happy birthday once again🎂🥳🎉🎊❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️ @melodyaanchal  @aanchal_2420
